Package com.mishmash.rally

Class Summary
Card Our basic item in a card game, and the building blocks of our hands.
CardMinnowShell This class handles the interactive shell prompt that is the interface for the game.
CardTest Tests methods in the Card class.
CardUtils A utilities class with only static methods to perform some simple but common actions in this class.
Hand This represents the fundamental purpose of the program, a 'hand' of cards.
HandEvaluator This is the all-knowing, all-powerful evaluation class of CardMinnow.
HandEvaluatorTest This is the most complicated and involved test class that is where is really bash on the system as a whole.
HandTest Tests some commonly used methods from the Hand class.
Interpreter This class interprets string input from the user and creates cards from that input if possible.
InterpreterTest Tests the tokenization and interpretation of user input.
Main Main class that just runs the program.
 

Enum Summary
Card.Suit This enumeration describes a suit.
Hand.HandType An enumeration for the different types of hands, given value according to increasing rank.
